      <p>I am a <span itemprop="nationality">Norwegian</span> generative
        artist. Most of my time is spent exploring the interesting results you
        can get from simple rules. Sometimes I <a href="#writing">write</a>
        about my work. If you have questions, I might have answered them already in the <a
          href="/faq/" onclick="ga('send', 'event', 'link', 'click',
          'faq');">FAQ</a>.

        <p>You can see a list of my exhibitions and talks <a href="/resume/"
            onclick="ga('send', 'event', 'link', 'click', 'Resume');">here</a>.
          I am also several other places on the internet:</p>

